Package: inpdfr
Type: Package
Title: Analyse Text Documents Using Ecological Tools
Version: 0.1.11
Author: Rebaudo Francois (IRD, UMR EGCE, IRD, CNRS, Univ. ParisSaclay)
Maintainer: Rebaudo Francois <francois.rebaudo@ird.fr>
